  "system": {
    "description": "<p>An heir of Siberys manifests a Siberys dragonmark—the rarest and most powerful form of a dragonmark—across his entire body. This grants the heir of Siberys a major @UUID[Compendium.swade-fantasy-companion.swade-fc-abilities.Item.LxomYrz417VxjMhA]{Innate Power} that can be activated once per day. If the power specifies one or more Power Modifiers, the power is always activated with those Power Modifiers unless stated otherwise. Using an Epic Modifier for this power does not require the @UUID[Compendium.swade-fantasy-companion.swade-fc-edges.Item.u6T4PbGGO1rmF2F0]{Epic Mastery} Edge.</p><table><colgroup><col></col><col></col></colgroup><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Mark</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Major Powers</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>Mark of Detection</p></td><td><p>Boost Trait (Moment of Prescience, self only)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Finding</p></td><td><p>Locate (Discern Location)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Handling</p></td><td><p>Awaken or <em>summon animal</em> (Increased Trait ×3)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Healing</p></td><td><p>Healing (Mass Healing)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Hospitality</p></td><td><p>Teleport (Refuge)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Making</p></td><td><p>Conjure item (Durable, True Creation, and (optionally) Major Creation)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Passage</p></td><td><p>Teleport (Greater Teleport)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Scribing</p></td><td><p>Illusion (documents with Duration, Permanent, and Strong)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Sentinel</p></td><td><p>Mind blank</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Shadow</p></td><td><p>Scrying (Greater Scrying)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Storm</p></td><td><p>Elemental manipulation (Weather)</p><p></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Mark of Warding</p></td><td><p>Barrier (Damage (solid wall), Deadly, Hardened, and Size)</p><p></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
